292
00:17:50,760 --> 00:17:52,040
It's cooked just right.

293
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:54,800
It smells so good.

294
00:18:10,400 --> 00:18:11,119
No fun.

295
00:18:11,199 --> 00:18:12,359
One has no appetite,

296
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:13,839
the other doesn't want to eat.

297
00:18:13,920 --> 00:18:14,719
I'm full too.

298
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:15,599
Then just throw it away.

299
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:30,319
Eating too much can cause indigestion.

300
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:32,959
I'll help, though it's a bit of a stretch for me.

301
00:18:33,199 --> 00:18:34,280
Thank you.

302
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:35,719
Ingredients.

303
00:18:35,760 --> 00:18:36,560
One Chiwen.

304
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:37,520
Cooking.

305
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:38,560
One Chiwen.

306
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:49,599
