307
00:18:51,319 --> 00:18:52,520
We didn't really do anything.

308
00:18:52,640 --> 00:18:53,560
Forget it if you don't want to talk.

309
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:55,119
It has nothing to do with me anyway.

310
00:18:57,280 --> 00:18:58,800
Wasting ingredients.

311
00:18:58,920 --> 00:19:00,239
Add one more Chiwen.

312
00:19:36,359 --> 00:19:37,400
Ridiculous.

313
00:19:38,040 --> 00:19:40,040
Why am I so angry?

314
00:20:17,479 --> 00:20:18,479
Throughout this journey,

315
00:20:18,959 --> 00:20:20,000
you've worked hard.

316
00:22:08,479 --> 00:22:09,839
What were you dreaming about this time?

317
00:22:26,040 --> 00:22:27,160
Do you want to eat it?

318
00:22:58,119 --> 00:22:58,839
Lu Jiu

319
00:22:59,079 --> 00:22:59,839
What's wrong?

320
00:23:00,119 --> 00:23:01,880
Are you having nightmares again?

321
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:03,920
Lu Jiu

322
00:23:16,560 --> 00:23:17,479
What's the matter?

323
00:23:22,479 --> 00:23:23,599
I was just...

324
00:23:24,359 --> 00:23:25,760
I thought I was dreaming.

325
00:23:26,439 --> 00:23:27,119
You...

326
00:23:27,199 --> 00:23:28,359
Did you dream about me?

327
00:23:29,839 --> 00:23:30,560
No.

328
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:31,599
I...

329
00:23:31,640 --> 00:23:32,839
I did dream about you.

330
00:23:32,920 --> 00:23:33,959
But not that kind of dream.

331
00:23:34,079 --> 00:23:35,199
It wasn't that kind of dream.

332
00:23:36,439 --> 00:23:38,199
I never said it was that kind of dream.

333
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:40,719
Linlang

334
00:23:41,520 --> 00:23:43,719
There's something I want to tell you.

335
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:46,239
The person who killed your father

336
00:23:46,560 --> 00:23:47,640
is from Tianluo.

337
00:23:48,119 --> 00:23:49,079
In this whole world,

338
00:23:49,359 --> 00:23:50,680
the only ones who can stand against Tianluo

339
00:23:51,119 --> 00:23:52,400
are the Diancha Division.

340
00:23:55,760 --> 00:23:56,920
Actually, I've always...

341
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:58,000
Me too.

342
00:24:01,079 --> 00:24:02,160
You too.

343
00:24:02,439 --> 00:24:03,400
Me too.

344
00:24:03,920 --> 00:24:05,719
I also consider you a good friend.

345
00:24:06,119 --> 00:24:07,319
And Sima Kong.

346
00:24:07,560 --> 00:24:09,000
We're all good friends.

347
00:24:16,599 --> 00:24:17,560
What did you do to her this time?

348
00:24:17,920 --> 00:24:19,280
What could I possibly do to her? I...

349
00:24:19,800 --> 00:24:20,839
I—I didn't do anything.

350
00:24:23,560 --> 00:24:24,479
Maybe...

351
00:24:25,719 --> 00:24:27,319
Maybe it's because I didn't do anything.

352
00:24:39,079 --> 00:24:39,920
Lu Jiu

353
00:24:40,119 --> 00:24:41,359
Don't blame me.

354
00:24:41,719 --> 00:24:44,199
I'm also trying to find out who killed my father.

355
00:24:53,599 --> 00:24:54,359
Are you okay?

356
00:24:54,439 --> 00:24:55,199
I'm fine.

357
00:25:25,000 --> 00:25:25,800
Lu Jiu

358
00:25:34,760 --> 00:25:35,680
Dislocated arm

359
00:25:35,760 --> 00:25:36,880
The tendon is also sprained

360
00:25:52,160 --> 00:25:53,079
What about Lu Jiu?

361
00:25:53,520 --> 00:25:55,000
Just feels too ashamed to see you

362
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:14,880
I'm sorry.

363
00:26:15,560 --> 00:26:16,239
I

364
00:26:16,520 --> 00:26:17,880
didn't mean to hurt you.

365
00:26:19,959 --> 00:26:21,160
This is for me.

366
00:26:25,719 --> 00:26:27,319
It's so far from the town here.

367
00:26:27,359 --> 00:26:28,599
You managed to come back so quickly.

368
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:29,599
It must have been tough on the way.

369
00:26:29,640 --> 00:26:30,400
I

370
00:26:30,599 --> 00:26:32,199
can only do this.

371
00:26:36,319 --> 00:26:37,079
Don't worry.

372
00:26:37,160 --> 00:26:38,920
This little injury is nothing.

373
00:26:39,119 --> 00:26:40,040
Don't forget,

374
00:26:40,079 --> 00:26:41,560
I'm a master at setting bones.

375
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:43,280
You don't have to comfort me.

376
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:44,880
I'm serious.

377
00:26:44,959 --> 00:26:46,239
When I was working on a case before,

378
00:26:46,359 --> 00:26:47,599
the human bones were brought back to the office.

379
00:26:47,719 --> 00:26:49,520
They happened to fall off the carriage.

380
00:26:49,640 --> 00:26:51,680
And then another passing carriage ran over them.

381
00:26:51,760 --> 00:26:52,839
They were scattered everywhere.

382
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:54,000
I managed to piece them all together.

383
00:26:54,079 --> 00:26:55,680
Tell me, am I amazing or not, Linlang?

384
00:26:56,520 --> 00:26:57,479
Can you

385
00:26:57,800 --> 00:26:59,959
stop pretending it's fine every time?

386
00:27:00,239 --> 00:27:01,359
If it weren't for me,

387
00:27:01,520 --> 00:27:02,719
you would have reached Mist Town long ago.

388
00:27:02,920 --> 00:27:04,160
No one would be chasing you.

389
00:27:04,239 --> 00:27:05,040
And you wouldn't have been hurt by me.

390
00:27:05,119 --> 00:27:06,479
None of this is your fault.

391
00:27:06,520 --> 00:27:08,160
But my mind is a mess right now.

392
00:27:08,479 --> 00:27:09,680
All my martial arts skills

393
00:27:09,920 --> 00:27:10,959
might

394
00:27:11,479 --> 00:27:12,560
come from

395
00:27:13,319 --> 00:27:15,079
a cold-blooded killer.

396
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:20,560
I

397
00:27:20,800 --> 00:27:21,959
don't want to hurt you.

398
00:27:22,560 --> 00:27:24,079
You'd better stay away from me.

399
00:27:31,959 --> 00:27:33,880
I won't let you become that kind of person.

400
00:27:35,079 --> 00:27:36,280
As long as I'm here,

401
00:27:36,839 --> 00:27:38,560
you won't forget the path you came from.

402
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:41,000
and you won't turn into a cold-blooded killer.

403
00:28:06,439 --> 00:28:08,040
It seems my beloved disciple

404
00:28:08,119 --> 00:28:10,640
is gradually regaining his memory.

405
00:28:11,319 --> 00:28:14,520
Then the clues to the treasure he found before losing his memory

406
00:28:15,119 --> 00:28:17,319
are about to be revealed as well.

407
00:28:18,119 --> 00:28:19,359
Send a message to Lu Kun

408
00:28:19,439 --> 00:28:20,439
and invite him for a meeting.

409
00:28:20,680 --> 00:28:21,280
Yes.

410
00:28:21,439 --> 00:28:22,640
Lord Dugu.

411
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:26,920
It's been a while, my lord. How have you been?

412
00:28:27,199 --> 00:28:29,400
Speak of the devil, and he appears.

413
00:28:29,640 --> 00:28:30,280
Brother Lu.

414
00:28:30,359 --> 00:28:33,000
It's been years. How is your health?

415
00:28:33,119 --> 00:28:34,000
I'm getting old.

416
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:36,040
If not for your great fortune,

417
00:28:36,119 --> 00:28:38,000
I probably wouldn't have lived to see today.

418
00:28:38,800 --> 00:28:40,239
You're too modest, Brother Lu.

419
00:28:40,319 --> 00:28:41,400
With your talent,

420
00:28:41,479 --> 00:28:43,040
even without associating with me,

421
00:28:43,119 --> 00:28:45,160
you could still achieve great things.

422
00:28:48,560 --> 00:28:50,880
Your health still hasn't improved, Brother Lu?

423
00:28:51,920 --> 00:28:53,239
At my age,

424
00:28:53,319 --> 00:28:54,119
all I wish for

425
00:28:54,359 --> 00:28:55,880
is to spend my remaining years under your protection,

426
00:28:56,199 --> 00:28:57,560
and live out my days in peace.

427
00:28:58,640 --> 00:28:59,079
Come,

428
00:28:59,319 --> 00:29:00,040
please have a seat.

429
00:29:00,439 --> 00:29:01,199
Sit, sit, sit.

430
00:29:01,280 --> 00:29:02,119
After you, my lord.

431
00:29:05,280 --> 00:29:06,880
It's getting cold as autumn sets in.

432
00:29:07,119 --> 00:29:08,479
You should take care.

433
00:29:09,079 --> 00:29:09,959
Servant!

434
00:29:10,359 --> 00:29:12,280
Bring the imperial wine bestowed by His Majesty

435
00:29:12,439 --> 00:29:13,560
and serve it to Brother Lu

436
00:29:13,640 --> 00:29:15,119
to warm him up.

437
00:29:15,520 --> 00:29:16,319
No, please.

438
00:29:16,560 --> 00:29:17,160
My lord,

439
00:29:17,280 --> 00:29:18,560
my body is weak

440
00:29:18,640 --> 00:29:19,959
and I'm afraid I can't drink alcohol.

441
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:21,280
Thank you, my lord.

442
00:29:22,479 --> 00:29:23,760
Then let's have tea instead.

443
00:29:27,959 --> 00:29:29,719
Brother Lu is in poor health.

444
00:29:29,839 --> 00:29:31,280
Yet he still has to set up a scheme.

445
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:33,599
To lure Fei Ying back to Mist Town.

446
00:29:34,040 --> 00:29:35,760
It's truly not easy.

447
00:29:36,959 --> 00:29:38,000
Sir, you see things clearly.

448
00:29:38,199 --> 00:29:40,719
For years, I have pretended to live in seclusion in Water City.

449
00:29:40,839 --> 00:29:43,000
But in fact, I've been working for you in Mist Town all along.

450
00:29:43,079 --> 00:29:45,319
I've never set up any scheme.

451
00:29:47,680 --> 00:29:49,800
Back then, when Fei Ying lost his memory,

452
00:29:50,199 --> 00:29:51,599
you and I made an agreement.

453
00:29:51,719 --> 00:29:54,280
We would act when the martial world was calm.

454
00:29:54,400 --> 00:29:56,079
And then plan this important matter.

455
00:29:56,719 --> 00:29:57,719
This matter

456
00:29:58,560 --> 00:30:00,800
is known to no one else.

457
00:30:01,719 --> 00:30:04,479
But someone interfered.

458
00:30:04,719 --> 00:30:08,680
Fei Ying almost fell into the hands of Geng Zhao from the Diancha Division.

459
00:30:10,239 --> 00:30:11,400
Tell me,

460
00:30:11,839 --> 00:30:13,640
what happened here?

461
00:30:15,599 --> 00:30:16,680
Heaven and earth can bear witness.

462
00:30:16,959 --> 00:30:19,439
I am absolutely loyal to you, sir.

463
00:30:19,959 --> 00:30:22,800
I know your loyalty well.

464
00:30:23,959 --> 00:30:25,040
Otherwise,

465
00:30:25,359 --> 00:30:29,640
you wouldn't have abandoned the thriving Fenglei Hall

466
00:30:29,719 --> 00:30:31,680
to join my Tianluo.

467
00:30:32,359 --> 00:30:33,319
Isn't that right?

468
00:30:35,839 --> 00:30:37,239
Li Chu.

469
00:31:08,520 --> 00:31:10,199
These three, including Lu Jiu,

470
00:31:10,359 --> 00:31:12,880
are now ranked third on the leaderboard.

471
00:31:13,359 --> 00:31:15,280
Wasn't the initial bounty just one hundred Chiwen?

472
00:31:15,359 --> 00:31:16,680
That's because at first,

473
00:31:16,760 --> 00:31:18,439
no one knew he could fight.

474
00:31:18,760 --> 00:31:20,599
Everyone thought he was just a spoiled young master.

475
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:23,119
Killing him would be as easy as killing a chicken.

476
00:31:23,319 --> 00:31:26,239
Who would have thought Lu Jiu actually possesses extraordinary martial arts.

477
00:31:26,280 --> 00:31:27,359
He's that powerful?

478
00:31:28,199 --> 00:31:28,880
So,

479
00:31:29,400 --> 00:31:30,959
is anyone still taking the job?

480
00:31:31,119 --> 00:31:32,280
I doubt it.

481
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:33,119
Most likely,

482
00:31:33,199 --> 00:31:35,000
it'll be just like Li Chu and Fei Ying.

483
00:31:35,280 --> 00:31:37,479
They've had bounties for years, but no one has accepted.

484
00:31:37,719 --> 00:31:39,439
By the way, Li Chu and Fei Ying—

485
00:31:39,680 --> 00:31:40,839
how many years have their bounties been up?

486
00:31:40,959 --> 00:31:42,000
Li Chu's bounty

487
00:31:42,280 --> 00:31:44,040
must have been there for at least twenty years.

488
00:31:44,199 --> 00:31:45,760
Fei Ying's has been six or seven years.

489
00:31:45,839 --> 00:31:47,040
The reward goes up every year,

490
00:31:47,119 --> 00:31:48,560
but still, no one takes the job.

491
00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:51,680
Do you think it's because their martial arts are too strong,

492
00:31:51,760 --> 00:31:53,520
or is it just impossible to find them?

493
00:31:53,640 --> 00:31:54,920
Probably both.

494
00:31:56,479 --> 00:31:57,800
The assassins who tried to kill them

495
00:31:58,119 --> 00:31:59,319
never came back.

496
00:32:00,439 --> 00:32:01,839
They all died.
